# Query Performance

- Use `select` with nested `select` — avoid `include` when only a few fields are needed
- Aggregate time-series in SQL (`$queryRaw` GROUP BY) instead of `findMany` + JS loops
- Dashboard reads: keep `Promise.all` in service; optimize each repository method
- Filter soft-deleted rows: spread `notDeleted` on all queries
- Date-range dashboards: rely on `@@index([status, paidAt])` on `Transaction`
- Serialize `Decimal` in services with `toNumber()`, not in repositories

See `.cursor/skills/barberpro-query-performance/SKILL.md` for examples.
